{"title":"Linux Server中搭建NAS存储服务(NFS)","uid":"28aab1e9215b73875e2b40964027aa9b","slug":"Linux-Server中搭建NAS存储服务-NFS","date":"2022-07-19T06:16:23.890Z","updated":"2022-07-21T05:13:05.573Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Linux-Server中搭建NAS存储服务-NFS.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<link rel=\"stylesheet\" class=\"aplayer-secondary-style-marker\" href=\"\\assets\\css\\APlayer.min.css\"><script src=\"\\assets\\js\\APlayer.min.js\" class=\"aplayer-secondary-script-marker\"></script><h2 id=\"关于命令-gquotacheck-cvug-x2F-dev-x2F-nas-x2F-nas1-报错没有生成aquota-user文件解决方法：\"><a href=\"#关于命令-gquotacheck-cvug-x2F-dev-x2F-nas-x2F-nas1-报错没有生成aquota-user文件解决方法：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"关于命令 gquotacheck -cvug &#x2F;dev&#x2F;nas&#x2F;nas1    报错没有生成aquota.user文件解决方法：\"></a>关于命令 gquotacheck -cvug &#x2F;dev&#x2F;nas&#x2F;nas1    报错没有生成aquota.user文件解决方法：</h2><h3 id=\"1、检查挂载后的文件类型是否和fstab文件中的一致\"><a href=\"#1、检查挂载后的文件类型是否和fstab文件中的一致\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1、检查挂载后的文件类型是否和fstab文件中的一致\"></a>1、检查挂载后的文件类型是否和fstab文件中的一致</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">mount | grep NAS\n##&#x2F;dev&#x2F;mapper&#x2F;nas-nas1 on &#x2F;NAS type ext3 (rw,relatime,seclabel,quota,usrquota,grpquota,stripe&#x3D;1024,data&#x3D;ordered)</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"1-1、如果不一致，请重新挂载\"><a href=\"#1-1、如果不一致，请重新挂载\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.1、如果不一致，请重新挂载\"></a>1.1、如果不一致，请重新挂载</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">cd\numount &#x2F;NAS\nmount -a\nmount | grep NAS</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"1-2、强制扫描已挂载的文件系统\"><a href=\"#1-2、强制扫描已挂载的文件系统\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.2、强制扫描已挂载的文件系统\"></a>1.2、强制扫描已挂载的文件系统</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">quotacheck -avug -mf</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"通过FTP访问NFS\"><a href=\"#通过FTP访问NFS\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"通过FTP访问NFS\"></a>通过FTP访问NFS</h2><h3 id=\"2、安装ftp软件包\"><a href=\"#2、安装ftp软件包\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2、安装ftp软件包\"></a>2、安装ftp软件包</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">yum install vsftpd ftp -y</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"2-1、修改-x2F-etc-x2F-vsftpd-x2F-vsftpd-conf配置文件\"><a href=\"#2-1、修改-x2F-etc-x2F-vsftpd-x2F-vsftpd-conf配置文件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.1、修改&#x2F;etc&#x2F;vsftpd&#x2F;vsftpd.conf配置文件\"></a>2.1、修改&#x2F;etc&#x2F;vsftpd&#x2F;vsftpd.conf配置文件</h3><p>创 建&#x2F;etc&#x2F;vsftpd&#x2F;chroot_list 文件：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">#vim &#x2F;etc&#x2F;vsftpd&#x2F;chroot_list\n\nuser1\nuser2\nuser3</code></pre>\n\n<p>修改&#x2F;etc&#x2F;vsftpd&#x2F;vsftpd.conf 配置文件：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">chroot_list_enable&#x3D;YES\t&#x2F;&#x2F;取消注释\n#(default follows) \t&#x2F;&#x2F;这个要注释掉，不然服务起不来（默认是注释的）\nchroot_list_file&#x3D;&#x2F;etc&#x2F;vsftpd&#x2F;chroot_list\t&#x2F;&#x2F;取消注释\n\n##最后一行添加\nallow_writeable_chroot&#x3D;YES</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"2-2、如果ftp登录不成功，修改-x2F-etc-x2F-pam-d-x2F-vsftpd配置文件\"><a href=\"#2-2、如果ftp登录不成功，修改-x2F-etc-x2F-pam-d-x2F-vsftpd配置文件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.2、如果ftp登录不成功，修改&#x2F;etc&#x2F;pam.d&#x2F;vsftpd配置文件\"></a>2.2、如果ftp登录不成功，修改&#x2F;etc&#x2F;pam.d&#x2F;vsftpd配置文件</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">#vim &#x2F;etc&#x2F;pam.d&#x2F;vsftpd\n\n注释掉auth require pam_shell.so</code></pre>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://s2.loli.net/2022/03/18/63VICkWSsOtKdbD.png\" alt=\"pam.d.png\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"2-3、登录测试\"><a href=\"#2-3、登录测试\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.3、登录测试\"></a>2.3、登录测试</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">ftp localhost</code></pre>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://s2.loli.net/2022/03/18/gY89D5S6jQTw3br.png\" alt=\"ftp.png\"></p>\n","text":"关于命令 gquotacheck -cvug &#x2F;dev&#x2F;nas&#x2F;nas1 报错没有生成aquota.user文件解决方法：1、检查挂载后的文件类型是否和fstab文件中的一致mount | grep NAS ##&#x2F;dev&#x2F;mapp...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":996,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Centos","slug":"Centos","count":7,"path":"api/categories/Centos.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"云计算基础架构与实践","slug":"云计算基础架构与实践","count":1,"path":"api/tags/云计算基础架构与实践.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8E%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4-gquotacheck-cvug-x2F-dev-x2F-nas-x2F-nas1-%E6%8A%A5%E9%94%99%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90aquota-user%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%9A\"><span class=\"toc-text\">关于命令 gquotacheck -cvug &#x2F;dev&#x2F;nas&#x2F;nas1    报错没有生成aquota.user文件解决方法：</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1%E3%80%81%E6%A3%80%E6%9F%A5%E6%8C%82%E8%BD%BD%E5%90%8E%E7%9A%84%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E5%92%8Cfstab%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E8%87%B4\"><span class=\"toc-text\">1、检查挂载后的文件类型是否和fstab文件中的一致</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1-1%E3%80%81%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C%E4%B8%8D%E4%B8%80%E8%87%B4%EF%BC%8C%E8%AF%B7%E9%87%8D%E6%96%B0%E6%8C%82%E8%BD%BD\"><span class=\"toc-text\">1.1、如果不一致，请重新挂载</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1-2%E3%80%81%E5%BC%BA%E5%88%B6%E6%89%AB%E6%8F%8F%E5%B7%B2%E6%8C%82%E8%BD%BD%E7%9A%84%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">1.2、强制扫描已挂载的文件系统</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87FTP%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AENFS\"><span class=\"toc-text\">通过FTP访问NFS</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2%E3%80%81%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85ftp%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6%E5%8C%85\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2、安装ftp软件包</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2-1%E3%80%81%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9-x2F-etc-x2F-vsftpd-x2F-vsftpd-conf%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2.1、修改&#x2F;etc&#x2F;vsftpd&#x2F;vsftpd.conf配置文件</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2-2%E3%80%81%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9Cftp%E7%99%BB%E5%BD%95%E4%B8%8D%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%EF%BC%8C%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9-x2F-etc-x2F-pam-d-x2F-vsftpd%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2.2、如果ftp登录不成功，修改&#x2F;etc&#x2F;pam.d&#x2F;vsftpd配置文件</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2-3%E3%80%81%E7%99%BB%E5%BD%95%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2.3、登录测试</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"H-MiKing","slug":"h-miking","avatar":"https://s2.loli.net/2022/03/09/hnWbjs6yMGKDXdk.jpg","link":"/","description":"新手博客，在校大学生，曾获得某省技能大赛一等奖。","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/H-MiKing","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/hjsuo","csdn":"https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_51369125?spm=1000.2115.3001.5343","juejin":"","customs":{"bilibili":{"icon":"/svg/bilibili.svg","link":"https://space.bilibili.com/346448962?spm_id_from=333.1007.0.0"}}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"Debian10的网络配置","uid":"63c71fba5e8a34529d9bdb3a5facfcb9","slug":"Debian10的网络配置","date":"2022-07-21T04:58:59.000Z","updated":"2022-07-21T05:01:07.494Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Debian10的网络配置.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"text":"网络配置一、配置文件方式1、编辑网卡配置文件interfaces vim &#x2F;etc&#x2F;network&#x2F;interfaces ... auto ens33 iface ens33 inet static address address 172.16.10...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":419,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Debian","slug":"Debian","count":1,"path":"api/categories/Debian.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Debian","slug":"Debian","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Debian.json"}],"author":{"name":"H-Mi